reviewText: Awesome documentary to have on your PSP. I just wish that they had the matches included. Maybe on a separate UMB or making it a double pack. Overall it's still an awesome little UMD to have for your collection.
Even though I purchased the item in the wrong format i've later found use for this particular item, when mailed i received the item on time and in over above perfect condition. 5 stars and up from me
Its awsome very recommended to all the Hart fans or to those who want to know about Wrestling History.
